---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Connect integrations — 1404 Mission Control"
  description="Connect QuickBooks Online, Microsoft 365, and Google Workspace to your Mission Control instance."
>
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 pt-40 pb-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-text-primary mb-4">Connect an integration</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-12">
      Mission Control is a multi-tenant platform. To connect QuickBooks Online, Microsoft 365,
      or Google Workspace to your account, go to your own Mission Control instance.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-bg-surface">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">1. Log in to your Mission Control</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          Your URL looks like <code class="text-copper">https://&#123;your-company&#125;.mc.1404.io</code> —
          check the welcome email from 1404 for the exact link.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-bg-surface">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">2. Open the Integrations page</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          Click <strong>Integrations</strong> in the left sidebar. You'll see cards for
          QuickBooks Online, Microsoft 365, and Google Workspace.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-bg-surface">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">3. Click Connect</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          Each card has a <strong>Connect</strong> button that starts the OAuth consent flow
          with the provider. For QBO and Google, you sign in directly. For Microsoft 365,
          your tenant admin receives a link to grant consent once for the whole tenant.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-bg-surface">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-text-primary mb-2">Need help?</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          Email <a href="mailto:holden@1404.io" class="text-copper hover:underline">holden@1404.io</a>
          or call <a href="tel:+12486071414" class="text-copper hover:underline">+1 (248) 607-1414</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
